  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective observational multicenter study in European ICUs. All patients admitted to the
      ICU for probable or confirmed Acute encephalitis (2013 IDSA - Infectious Disease Society of
      America criteria) will be included. Factors associated with a poor prognosis will be
      identified by multivariate analysis using a logistic regression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
